org.semanticweb.rulewerk.core.model.api

Interface LanguageStringConstant

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Constant, Entity, Term
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    LanguageStringConstantImpl

    public interface LanguageStringConstant
extends Constant
    Interface for string constants with a language tag, used to represent values of type http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#langString in RDF, OWL, and related languages used with knowledge graphs. Such terms are of type TermType.LANGSTRING_CONSTANT.
    Author:
    Markus Kroetzsch

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods Default Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      default String getDatatype()
      Returns the datatype of this term, which is always http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#langString.
      String getLanguageTag()
      Returns the language tag of the literal, which should be a lowercase string that conforms to the BCP 47 specification.
      String getString()
      Returns the string value of the literal without the language tag.
      default TermType getType()
      Return the type of this term.
